ume啲手足袋住觀星筆同切餅刀係用嚟攻擊人嘅武器有咩分別?<br />\n更何況你根本唔知佢係咪袋住把刀<br />\n佢拎住把刀出嚟fing下fing下就話啫"},{"pid":"1cc62a8c1e567876a4c3e19b1a7b6acfc8318ce9","tid":1739129,"uid":127694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"大大力推"},{"pid":"2a77638fbaf77f44659407640f9819ef5e3e6c1b","tid":1739129,"uid":217688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"4e03b53ed88d58e246f879bcfde982d7fe7a00f3","tid":1739129,"uid":44412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:20:41.000Z","msg":"推!<br />\n不過第3點都有少少保留<br />\n尤其係諗起荃灣俾人斬手斬腳既手足"},{"pid":"2d40beffa717370fbf1785d34df0ec438b9856c4","tid":1739129,"uid":44412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T23:23:50.000Z","msg":"推"}]}